# BuildKit uses this in place of the repo-root .dockerignore for darwin.Dockerfile
# (the root one is scoped to the website/Railway build and excludes everything but
# website/ + packages/core, which starves the sidecar cross-build of rust-toolchain.toml,
# crates, Cargo.toml, etc.). Send the full source; drop only artifacts/caches the
# in-container build regenerates (pnpm install + cargo build happen inside the image).
.git
**/node_modules
**/target
**/dist
**/.astro
**/.turbo
